Misonyeon

Native name:

Introduction

Misonyeon is a South Korean R&B and hip-hop soloist who debuted on February 20, 2020, with the single "I Go," featuring seizetheday. Known for his emotional vocals and heartfelt music, he is signed with ANDME and continues to release captivating tracks. Currently, no personal details about him, such as his real name or background, are publicly available.
